
(i) Create a conda environment
Command: conda create -n tf2 --clone base

(ii) Activate the conda environment.
Command: conda activate tf2

(iii) Install Tensorflow 2.0
 pip install tensorflow
 
(iv)Test the installation
Command: python -c “import tensorflow as tf”

(v) Deactivate the environment to go to base environment
Command: conda deactivate
